<div id="support" class="box">
<h3>Support</h3>
<p>First you should read the existing <a href="#documentation">documentation</a> before asking any questions.</p>
<p>Support or feature requests, bugs and patches can be submitted using the <a href="http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?group_id=214758">AJAX Chat Tracking System</a>.</p>
<p>Other topics related to AJAX Chat can be discussed using the <a href="http://sourceforge.net/forum/?group_id=214758">AJAX Chat project forums</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Please do not send e-mails or private messages to the developers for support requests.</strong></p>
</div>
