<p><strong>Please note:</strong><br />AJAX Chat has been founded and developed as a one-man project up to version 0.8.1.2 by <a href="https://blueimp.net">Sebastian Tschan</a>.<br />
He is not actively involved in the development process any more, so please do not send him any e-mails or private messages regarding AJAX Chat.</p>
<p>Many thanks to Phil for continuing this project!</p>
