<div id="localizations" class="box">
<h3>Localizations</h3>
<p>Inlcudes Arabic, Brazilian Portuguese, Bulgarian, Catalan, Chinese (Simplified and Traditional), Croatian, Czech, Dutch, English, Finnish, French, German, Greek, Hebrew, Indonesian, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Norwegian, Polish, Romanian, Russian, Serbian, Slovak, Slovenian, Spanish, Swedish, Turkish and Ukrainian translations.</p>
<p>Thanks to the <a href="http://ajax-chat.wiki.sourceforge.net/Localization#tocLocalization3">translators.</a></p>
<p>If you want to contribute please read the instructions on the <a href="http://ajax-chat.wiki.sourceforge.net/Localization">AJAX Chat Localization Wikipage</a>.</p>
</div>
